   \verb{h_ch} \tab Constant hazards estimate of... hazard. The most basic hazard estimate where the number of events is Poisson distributed. \tab \verb{n_events/t_at_risk} \tab \verb{sqrt(h_ch_est/t_at_risk)} \cr
